text: Ðis seond ða londgemære æt Wulfferdinlea.
Up efter broce, on ðone aldan hæge.
Ondlong hæges, on ðone aldan weg.
Ondlang weges on ða miclan strete.
<../images/tbar.gif>swa on calcbroc ondlong broces<../images/tbar.gif>swa on horsa broc.
Eft of sture on ða dic ondlong dices<../images/tbar.gif>on cuþdredestreo.
Of heahsecan berge on ða dic.
Ondlong dices on Wenferð ondlong Wenferþ<../images/tbar.gif>æft on sture.
